  "instructions": [
    "Heat vegetable oil in a slate tile pot over medium heat until shimmering.",
    "Add minced ginger and garlic and sauté until fragrant, about 30 seconds.",
    "Add diced onion, carrot, and celery and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in tamarind paste, fish sauce, and sugar, then pour in 4 cups of vegetable broth and bring to a gentle boil.",
    "Add trimmed Chinese long beans and simmer until tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in lime juice, adjust seasoning with salt if needed, and add diced tomato, cooking for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Remove from heat, ladle soup into bowls, and garnish with fresh herbs."
